	abstract = {The integration of artificial intelligence (AI) in events and festivals has resulted in significant advancements in enhancing operational efficiency, attendee experience, and overall event management. This chapter explores several cases where AI technologies have been successfully implemented, showcasing their impact on diverse aspects of event organization. Key examples include AI-powered chatbots that provide real-time information and support to attendees, predictive analytics tools that forecast attendance and optimize resource allocation, and AI-driven personalization engines that tailor experiences to individual preferences. Additionally, AI-based security systems have improved crowd management and safety, while automated content creation tools have enriched event marketing and engagement. These implementations not only streamline event operations but also create more immersive and interactive experiences for participants. By examining these successful cases, the chapter highlights the transformative potential of AI in the events and festivals industries and provides insights into best practices for leveraging AI technologies to achieve event and festival goals and enhance attendee satisfaction.},
